   SPRINT _ Sprint and MCI WorldCom hold a news conference to
discuss their merger filing with the FCC. By Kevin Murphy and Ted
Sickinger
</P>
<P>
   BLOCK _ A new agreement with the IRS will help streamline H&AMP;R
Block's Rapid Refund program. By Gene Meyer
</P>
<P>
   STAFF _ Ownership of nearly half of all family-owned businesses
is expected to change hands within the next five years. Lots of
financial and emotional guidance is needed to ease the transfer of
wealth and responsibility from one generation to the next. At Work
column. By Diane Stafford
</P>
