<DOCNO> NYT19991117.0113 </DOCNO>
<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-11-17 13:58 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A2523 &Cx1f; ttc-z
r e BC-GIFTS-IDEAS-LADN &LR;      11-17 0907
