   THOMPSON-COLUMN &QL;
</P>
<P>
   UNDATED _ Here's shocking news: A federal judge in California
predicted the other day that those new laws prohibiting banks from
charging fees for using their ATMs will turn out to be
unconstitutional. Who woulda guessed? By BILL THOMPSON. Story has
moved in ``k'' commentary category. &QL; 
 &QL; 
 &QL; 
