 &HT;    Spotlight this week
 &HT;    By Steve Murray
 &HT;    c. 1999 Cox News Service
<TEXT>
<P>
   Heather Graham (`Austin Powers: The Spy Who Shagged Me')
</P>
<P>
   &QR;  ``Drugstore Cowboy'' (1989; R) _ As a baby-faced drifter who
falls in with druggie Matt Dillon and company.
</P>
<P>
   &QR;  ``Swingers'' (1996; R) _ Turning up as the ideal girl on the
dance floor in this wry comedy.
</P>
<P>
   &QR;  ``Boogie Nights'' (1997; R) _ Proving you gotta have a gimmick
as Rollergirl in this porn-industry epic.
</P>
<P>
   &QR;  ``Scream 2'' (1997; R) _ Playing the Drew Barrymore role in
this sly flick's film-within-a-film.
</P>
<P>
   &QR;  ``Two Girls and a Guy'' (1998; R) _ She's one of the girls,
and her sex scene with Robert Downey Jr. almost got the film rated
NC-17.
</P>
<P>
   &QR;  ``Lost in Space'' (1998; PG-13) _ Trying not to get eclipsed
by the so-so special FX.
</P>
<P>
   _Steve Murray
</P>
<P>
   THE VIDEO COLLECTOR
</P>
