<P>
   RUSSIA-PIPELINE (Moscow) _ Behind the jockeying between
President Clinton and Boris Yeltsin lies an issue that has
influenced US-Russian relations for years _ the huge pipeline from
Caspian oilfields that may enrich Turkey and change relations along
Russia's volatile southern rim. By David Filipov. 1000 words.
</P>
<P>
   w/
</P>
<P>
   RUSSIA-CLINTON (Moscow) _ President Clinton prepares for his big
Chechnya pow-wow with Russian leader Boris Yeltsin. By Susan
Milligan. 750 words.
