<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-11-17 19:36 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A2943 &Cx1f; tth-z
r v BC-BUDGET-SPI &LR;      11-17 0161
</HEADER>
<BODY>
