<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-11-17 21:15 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A3079 &Cx1f; ttc-z
r d BC-MILLENNIUM-MAIN-LADN 4takes &LR;    11-17 1563
