<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-11-17 21:47 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A3127 &Cx1f; tad-z
u f BC-KFC18-COX     11-17 0180
</HEADER>
