   &UR;  &QL;  &LR; 
 &UR; SCHWAB _  &LR; IPO road shows _ in which soon-to-be-public companies
make their pitch to big-bucks institutional investors _ are finally
going to be open to individual investors as well. Well, the richer
ones anyway. San Francisco's Charles Schwab Corp. has received a
green light from the Securities and Exchange Commission to
broadcast road show proceedings via the Internet. By David Lazarus
</P>
